{"build_type":"library","module_name":"reap-ring-slots-iteration","package_name":"reap-ring-slots-iteration","description":"Design 4.4b reaper walk: tail-recursively scan the as-completed block-ring [i,head). For each non-null slot, read the worker block (rp[6]); in blocking mode reap unconditionally (recycle-worker-arena-block-into-recycled-pool waits the gone-edge), else peek the block's CLEARTID word (block[80], byte640) and reap only if the worker thread has exited (0). Nulls each reaped slot so it is reaped once. Mirrors collect-result-pointer-array-into-document-sequence's tail-recursion (TCO, constant stack).","function_definitions":{"reap-ring-slots-iteration":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"block_ring","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"i","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"head","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"blocking","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"six","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":6},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i80","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":80},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":">=","lhs":{"value":"i"},"rhs":{"value":"head"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"rp","base":"block_ring","index":"i","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"rp"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on